Hoist continued his work, letting out a chuckle, "Ahhh yes, quite." he
said, still sounding friendly. There was the problem. "Now Sludge, don't
strugle, this will hurt a little bit, but it will be much better after."
with that, his rocket launcher arm came up, and he gently positioned it
at a flat surface at Sludges head. It then emited a low power laser, and
began to open a hole.
